These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, milk, 7up, juice
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, yellow, mauve, azure
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, ship, subway, van
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the van is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person who likes mauve is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
7. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | coffee    | 7up      | milk      | juice    |
| Color   | azure | blood-red | yellow | mauve |
| Transport     | ship    | van       | subway     | bus     |

