.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bongani, vegafina, dannemann
City: berlin, liverpool, london, edinburgh
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, romance, superhero, thriller
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
7. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar          | pall-mall     | dannemann     | bongani       | vegafina    |
| City         | liverpool | london   | berlin | edinburgh |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller    | superhero | romance    | epic        |

