.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, pony, horse
There are 4 different nationalities: british, dutch, malaysian, polish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, time-travel, adventure
1. the dutch is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the british##3
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Pet      | ferret | guinea-pig  | pony    | horse |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | british  | dutch    |
| Movie-Genre         | comedy    | adventure | action | time-travel  |

