.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
House: tower, modern, farmhouse, townhouse
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, fanta, 7up
4 different pets are kept: dog, goat, lizard, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is between the person drinking coffee and the tower house##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the townhouse house##1
6. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
7. the townhouse house is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
8. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the modern house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| House          | farmhouse   | tower     | modern | townhouse |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up | milk   | coffee     |
| Pet           | turtle | lizard      | goat     | dog       |

