.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, cat, turtle, chinchilla
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia, begonia, tulip
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, romance, western
1. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
3. the person who growsbegonia is the person watching action movies##1
4. the person who growszinnia is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the cat##2
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
8. the owner of the turtle is the person watching romance movies##1
9. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet          | turtle      | chinchilla | cat      | pony |
| Flower           | dahlia | zinnia | tulip | begonia   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance    | western   | drama     | action   |

