City: edinburgh, rome, berlin, paris
1. the person traveling to rome is the coach##1
2. the person traveling to berlin is the craftsman house##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the tower house is on the left or right of the person traveling to berlin##3
5. the colonial house is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
