.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, traveling, writing
4 different pets are kept: horse, dog, frog, fish
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, zucchini, papaya, cranberry
 1. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
 2. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
 4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 5. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 6. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 8. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
 9. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
10. the owner of the dog is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
11. the owner of the dog is the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | traveling    | camping  | gardening | writing   |
| Pet           | fish | dog   | frog    | horse |
| Food   | cranberry      | papaya | zucchini | grapefruit  |

