2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Pet          | bird | hamster    | fish | hedgehog    |
| Hobby         | hiking     | magic-tricks | dancing  | board-games |
| Beverage   | 7up    | mirinda      | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk         |

