4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bongani, tiparillo, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, september, june
1. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is between the person drinking coffee and the montecristo-smoker##2
3. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
5. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
6. the person drinking coffee is the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person who's birthday is in september is the montecristo-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | coffee      | almond-milk | milk       | iced-tea  |
| Cigar       | tiparillo | oliveros | montecristo    | bongani |
| Birthday   | july     | february         | september | june     |

