1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking coffee is the person traveling to hannover##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the wooden house##1
4. the gothic-revival house is between the wooden house and the craftsman house##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | juice   | lemonade    | coffee      | almond-milk |
| City       | colone  | berlin | hannover | venice     |
| House   | wooden | gothic-revival        | craftsman  | ranch-style        |

