.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-18::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, video-games, collecting, singing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, june, february
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, helicopter, skateboard, van
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person driving the skateboard##2
3. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Hobby      | singing      | collecting     | video-games | drawing |
| Birthday   | june    | december    | february   | march |
| Transport     | skateboard | helicopter | van   | car    |

