.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, blueberry, cranberry, plum
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, red, mauve, chestnut
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, brazilian, mexican, egyptian
1. the person eating plum is on the left or right of the chinese##3
2. the brazilian is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
3. the mexican is the person eating plum##1
4. the person eating cranberry is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
5. the brazilian is between the person eating avocado and the person eating cranberry##2
6. the chinese is on the left or right of the person who likes chestnut##3
7. the mexican is on the far right##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Food    | cranberry | blueberry  | avocado  | plum           |
| Color     | brown | mauve | red   | chestnut |
| Nationality   | egyptian   | brazilian       | chinese | mexican  |

 